description: In November 2011 Yvette Avenue Productions released Vigilante Project: The Confessional. It is a short, 9-page book which served as a preview for the upcoming Vigilante Project series. This issue picks up in the middle of our story in order to showcase the character, his costume, weapons, and abilities.
name: The Confessional

description: In Vigilante Project #3 Alvin Gentry follows his first big lead, but struggles to get the rest of his life back to normal. They say that you cant go home again, but that wont stop Alvin from trying. The rabbit hole gets deeper as the stakes get higher.
name: Homecoming
